    "description": "Magna Graecia 是一款轻松的益智游戏，具有古希腊设计的城市建设元素。 通过放置房屋并获得新瓷砖来扩展您的村庄。 战略性地放置您的建筑物和资源并获得邻接奖励。 形成三角形以升级您的建筑物并获得更好的收益。 最后，收集橄榄和葡萄以解锁更多房屋。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566830/extras/fc37788d6fa393d29f7966ce27c337dd.poster.avif?t=1767811850\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566830/extras/fc37788d6fa393d29f7966ce27c337dd.webm?t=1767811850\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566830/extras/fc37788d6fa393d29f7966ce27c337dd.mp4?t=1767811850\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>扩展您的村庄，获得邻接奖励并形成三角形</strong></h2><br>每一回合你都会获得一个随机的建筑或资源——从橄榄农场到麦田。 房子将所有相邻的瓷砖添加到您的村庄。 当相同类型的建筑物彼此相邻时，您会获得奖励——建造集群以获得更好的奖励。 您可以通过将 3 个相同类型的对象组成三角形来升级您的建筑物和资源，每个对象都与另外两个相邻。 等级越高，收益越高！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566830/extras/47b5dc9aaab31487d3726b3311092a6a.poster.avif?t=1767811850\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566830/extras/47b5dc9aaab31487d3726b3311092a6a.webm?t=1767811850\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566830/extras/47b5dc9aaab31487d3726b3311092a6a.mp4?t=1767811850\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>收集橄榄和葡萄以解锁更多房屋</strong></h2><br>Magna Graecia 有两种资源——橄榄和葡萄。 作为交换，您可以获得额外的房屋并继续扩大村庄。 橄榄和葡萄田生产这些资源，而农场则收集它们。 要获得橄榄和葡萄，您需要将农场和田地放在一起。 每个邻接会给你1个橄榄/葡萄。 您的农场和田地的级别越高，您获得的资源就越多！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566830/extras/e637d7bcb8fc6b9128addda3529be32e.poster.avif?t=1767811850\" width=600 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566830/extras/e637d7bcb8fc6b9128addda3529be32e.webm?t=1767811850\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566830/extras/e637d7bcb8fc6b9128addda3529be32e.mp4?t=1767811850\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566830/extras/7aab04377b474ac1a06590fbc8ead91e.poster.avif?t=1767811850\" width=600 height=56 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566830/extras/7aab04377b474ac1a06590fbc8ead91e.webm?t=1767811850\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566830/extras/7aab04377b474ac1a06590fbc8ead91e.mp4?t=1767811850\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
